esqlQuery.esql:
// Alert triggers when the memory_grants_pending exceeds the recommended threshold value {0} within the look back time window.
// The alert is grouped by Server Name.
// You can adjust the threshold value by modifying the memory_grants_pending in the WHERE clause 
 FROM metrics-microsoft_sqlserver.performance-default
| STATS memory_grants_pending=MAX(mssql.metrics.memory_grants_pending) by mssql.metrics.server_name
| WHERE memory_grants_pending > 0
